        public void nextGeneration(int start,
                           int stop)
        Next generation, counts neighbours and sets next generation. If there is less than two neighbours the cell dies. Cells with two or three neighbours continues to live. Cells with more than three neighbours die. If a dead cell is surrounded with 3 alive cells, it becomes alive.
